{"type": "article", "id": 15465, "title": "The Mòltair手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-24T06:34:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143505Ykh4Qq7GpjAJni02.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦设计师 Samuel Wilkinson 和苏格兰钟表品牌 Nomad 合作发布了一组手表，正在伦敦设计周上展示。这款表有一个非常大的指针却没有刻度，长方形的指针随时间变化将圆形的表盘分割成不同角度的扇形，它们之间构成有趣的几何图案，也使这款表有很强的装饰效果。不锈钢的圆形表有黑色、银色和金色三种颜色，搭配黑色的皮质表带，男女皆可使用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142548VKBtEwjA0oca7ubH.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"312\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142548SHjB2wyeJPTq4NWb.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"348\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74358974\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261425491yOKcGfpPvIRguZ4.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"387\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82692308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261425493g80Q5d6OXWcjhil.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"312\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}